# Security-sensitive environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.sample

# Private keys and certificate bundles
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa
id_ed25519

# Common secret/config artifacts
secrets.*
credentials.*

# Build output and dependencies (root-level safety net)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
